summary: Every time Hawkeye (Kate Bishop) appears in Civil War (2006-2007) not including side comics (Civil War Files, Civil War Battle...
caption:
Every time Hawkeye (Kate Bishop) appears in Civil War (2006-2007) not including side comics (Civil War Files, Civil War Battle Damage Report, Civil War: The Initiative or Civil War: Young Avengers & Runaways). She appears 30 times, which is more than any of the Young Avengers except for Patriot. This is the first post because you can’t put 30 images in one.

NOTES: In first two images Kate is a complete badass. Just look at her! It’s all in her glasses, which she loses somewhere during Young Avengers’ arrest. The next time she wears them is during the battle in Prison 42, so we have an opportunity to look at her expressions more. She looks very fragile in later images and is grinning widely in the fifth one. The last one has four shadowed figures which are Kate, Billy, Vision and the Falcon.
